#

Pan-Seared Cod with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$15
520 kcal

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SeafoodComfort FoodHeartyDinner

Description

Succulent cod fillets seared to perfection, served alongside creamy garlic mashed potatoes for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Cod fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Yukon gold potatoes: 2 large
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Unsweetened almond milk: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
